@page "/platform"

@*
    Standalone portal page hosting the platform stats section (issue #1692). Kept as its own route
    so the stats panel is fully additive - it does not alter the agent dashboard or chat surface -
    while still being reachable in the portal at /platform.
*@

<PageTitle>BotNexus &mdash; Platform</PageTitle>

<div class="platform-config-page">
    <header class="platform-config-toolbar">
        <h2>&#x1F4CA; Platform</h2>
    </header>

    <div class="config-page">
        <div class="config-panel-canvas">
            <PlatformStatsPanel />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
